text:
‘Bill Nye, the I don’t know why guy’ and Tucker Carlson talk climate change Posted at 10:19 pm on February 27, 2017 by William A. 
On Monday’s show, Fox News’ Tucker Carlson had Bill Nye the Science Guy on to talk about climate change: Got to hang out w @BillNye before going on @TuckerCarlson He told me about https://t.co/NnIYVEIUYo how we get to 100% renewable energy pic.twitter.com/Xk1Yp6XgHP 
— Jared Polis (@jaredpolis) February 28, 2017 . @BillNye : Climate change skeptics suffer from cognitive dissonance on global warming. #Tucker pic.twitter.com/qHQ3YcuLeZ 
— Fox News (@FoxNews) February 28, 2017 . @BillNye : “The evidence for climate change is overwhelming.” #Tucker pic.twitter.com/l2unJCRBfA 
— Fox News (@FoxNews) February 28, 2017 . @BillNye : “The speed that climate change is happening is caused by humans.” #Tucker pic.twitter.com/cQiIFCYrtu 
— Fox News (@FoxNews) February 28, 2017 #Tucker to @BillNye What would the climate look like right now with out human activity? -TCT @FoxNews 
— Tucker Carlson (@TuckerCarlson) February 28, 2017 Trending
